default2.3.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultRestrictive national policy:
default  
defaultIn some cases, national policy is restricted to too narrow a field.  
defaultFor instance, the lack of a 
defaultmandatory 
defaultobligation 
defaultto 
defaultreimburse local CT operators running Section 19 services at separate fares for transporting eligible 
defaultconcessionary passengers means that many CT operators end up subsidising these passengers themselves.
